Ok heres a new source of harry potter which contains english subs when needed now :)

The source was very dark in places,but also very bright in light scenes,so needed alot of work.

Firstly we had to rotate and level the video up and then crop all unwanted borders etc....then we

moved onto the brightness,contrast and colouring ...which we also tweaked.

Now like we said the bright scenes were very bright and the one @ 1hr 31mins you couldn't see anything,so

for that part we had to take the russian cam and add it into our encode....last around 5mins.

After all that it was down to syncing it and what a pita it was ...due too dark scenes and other things

some parts were dam hard to sync,but i think we got most if not all of it sorted :)



Anyway enjoy a new source folks :)
